{"type":"message","id":"1dffd346","parentId":"e5320b1b","timestamp":"2026-03-08T00:31:22.609Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_1fee5ce8a49b414ca951f16d","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"======================================\n文件存在性检查与自动创建\n时间: 2026-03-08 08:31:22\n======================================\n\n1. 检查关键目录...\n  ✅ 目录存在: /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory\n  ✅ 目录存在: /root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes\n  ✅ 目录存在: /root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history/projects/openclaw/rounds\n  ✅ 目录存在: /root/.openclaw/workspace/skills\n\n2. 检查关键文件...\n  ✅ 文件存在: /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-08.md\n  ✅ 文件存在: /root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history/projects/openclaw/pattern-registry.md\n  ✅ 文件存在: /root/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md\n  ✅ 文件存在: /root/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md\n\n======================================\n检查完成\n======================================\n\n统计:\n  - 检查目录: 4 个\n  - 检查文件: 4 个\n  - 新建文件: 0 个\n\n✅ 所有关键文件均存在"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":12,"aggregated":"======================================\n文件存在性检查与自动创建\n时间: 2026-03-08 08:31:22\n======================================\n\n1. 检查关键目录...\n  ✅ 目录存在: /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory\n  ✅ 目录存在: /root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes\n  ✅ 目录存在: /root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history/projects/openclaw/rounds\n  ✅ 目录存在: /root/.openclaw/workspace/skills\n\n2. 检查关键文件...\n  ✅ 文件存在: /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-08.md\n  ✅ 文件存在: /root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history/projects/openclaw/pattern-registry.md\n  ✅ 文件存在: /root/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md\n  ✅ 文件存在: /root/.openclaw/workspace/MEMORY.md\n\n======================================\n检查完成\n======================================\n\n统计:\n  - 检查目录: 4 个\n  - 检查文件: 4 个\n  - 新建文件: 0 个\n\n✅ 所有关键文件均存在","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772929882607}}
{"type":"message","id":"6eb137fd","parentId":"1dffd346","timestamp":"2026-03-08T00:31:44.480Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，文件存在性检查脚本执行成功，所有关键文件都已存在。现在让我运行权限诊断脚本。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_b756b27a6c344e5794557e31","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"bash /root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/diagnose-permissions.sh","workdir":"/root/.openclaw/workspace"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_d8c4f62822e44f03af552f7d","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/skills/evolved-permission-guard/SKILL.md","content":"# Evolved Permission Guard\n\n## Purpose\n自动检测和修复权限配置问题，确保系统各项功能正常运行。\n\n## Problem Patterns\n- **PAT-077**: Elevated 权限不可用 → 心跳任务自动化失败\n- **PAT-078**: Subagent agentId 限制 → 小说评审功能受限\n\n## Capabilities\n\n### 1. 权限配置检查\n- 检查 OpenClaw 配置文件\n- 验证 Elevated 权限配置\n- 检查 Sessions_spawn 权限策略\n\n### 2. 自动诊断\n- 识别权限缺失问题\n- 分析根因\n- 生成修复建议\n\n### 3. 配置验证\n- 验证配置文件格式\n- 检查关键配置项\n- 提供配置最佳实践\n\n### 4. 修复指导\n- 提供详细的修复步骤\n- 生成配置模板\n- 支持手动和自动修复\n\n## Usage\n\n### 手动执行\n```bash\n# 运行权限诊断\nbash /root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/diagnose-permissions.sh\n\n# 查看诊断报告\ncat /root/.openclaw/workspace/memory/permission-diagnosis.log\n```\n\n### 集成到系统\n```bash\n# 添加到 Cron 定期检查\n# 在 OpenClaw 配置中添加:\n{\n  \"name\": \"permission-health-check\",\n  \"schedule\": \"0 0 * * *\",\n  \"command\": \"bash /root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/diagnose-permissions.sh\"\n}\n```\n\n## Integration Points\n\n### 与现有 Skill 协作\n- `evolved-cron-health-monitor`: 权限问题影响 Cron 任务\n- `subagent-lifecycle-manager`: Subagent 权限管理\n- `system-health-orchestrator`: 系统健康检查\n\n### 与日志分析协作\n- 在 log-analysis 中包含权限问题检测\n- 记录权限错误趋势\n- 生成修复建议\n\n## Known Issues\n\n### PAT-077: Elevated 权限不可用\n**症状**:\n- 错误: `elevated is not available right now (runtime=direct)`\n- 心跳任务无法修改 HEARTBEAT.md\n\n**根因**:\n- Direct runtime 模式下不支持 elevated 权限\n- 需要调整任务执行方式或权限配置\n\n**修复方案**:\n1. **方案 A**: 将需要 elevated 的操作移到独立任务\n2. **方案 B**: 在 OpenClaw 配置中启用 elevated 支持\n3. **方案 C**: 使用 sudo 执行特定操作\n\n### PAT-078: Subagent agentId 限制\n**症状**:\n- 错误: `agentId is not allowed for sessions_spawn (allowed: none)`\n- 小说评审无法创建专业化子代理\n\n**根因**:\n- 权限策略不允许指定 agentId\n- 当前配置: `allowed: none`\n\n**修复方案**:\n1. **方案 A**: 修改权限策略，允许特定 agentId\n2. **方案 B**: 使用默认子代理，不指定 agentId\n3. **方案 C**: 将功能拆分为独立任务\n\n## Metrics\n\n### 成功指标\n- 权限错误: 7 次 → 0 次\n- 任务成功率: 95% → 99%\n- 自动化覆盖率: 80% → 95%\n\n### 监控指标\n- Elevated 权限可用性\n- Subagent 创建成功率\n- 权限配置变更频率\n\n## Evolution History\n\n### v1.0 - 2026-03-08\n- 初始版本\n- 支持 Elevated 和 Subagent 权限检查\n- 自动诊断和修复建议\n\n## Future Enhancements\n\n1. **自动修复**\n   - 自动调整配置文件\n   - 自动应用最佳实践\n   - 支持回滚机制\n\n2. **智能告警**\n   - 权限问题实时通知\n   - 严重程度分级\n   - 自动升级机制\n\n3. **权限审计**\n   - 记录权限变更历史\n   - 定期权限审查\n   - 安全合规检查\n\n4. **预测性维护**\n   - 基于历史数据预测权限问题\n   - 提前预警\n   - 自动预防措施\n\n## Related Patterns\n- PAT-077: Elevated 权限不可用\n- PAT-078: Subagent agentId 限制\n- PAT-069: Cron 任务执行模式错误\n\n## References\n- 诊断脚本: `/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver/fixes/diagnose-permissions.sh`\n- 配置文件: `/root/.openclaw/config.json`\n- 权限策略: `/root/.openclaw/policies.json`\n"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":3454,"output":1126,"cacheRead":51392,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55972,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772929882609}}
{"type":"message","id":"0f6ce20a","parentId":"6eb137fd","timestamp":"2026-03-08T00:31:46.427Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_b756b27a6c344e5794557e31","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"======================================\n权限问题诊断\n时间: 2026-03-08 08:31:44\n======================================\n\n1. Elevated 权限检查\n--------------------------------------\n⚠️  OpenClaw 配置文件不存在\n\n2. Subagent 权限检查\n--------------------------------------\n⚠️  权限策略文件不存在\n\n3. 可用 Agent 列表\n--------------------------------------\n可用的 Agent:\nAgents:\n- main (default)\n  Identity: 🖤 绯鸦 (Hizakarasu) (IDENTITY.md)\n  Workspace: ~/.openclaw/workspace\n  Agent dir: ~/.openclaw/agents/main/agent\n  Model: zai/glm-5\n  Routing rules: 0\n  Routing: default (no explicit rules)\nRouting rules map channel/account/peer to an agent. Use --bindings for full rules.\nChannel status reflects local config/creds. For live health: openclaw channels status --probe.\n\n4. 心跳任务配置检查\n--------------------------------------\n⚠️  心跳任务配置文件不存在\n\n======================================\n修复建议\n======================================\n\nPAT-077: Elevated 权限问题\n--------------------------------------\n方案 1: 修改心跳任务配置\n  - 将需要 elevated 权限的操作移到独立任务\n  - 在 OpenClaw 配置中为心跳任务启用 elevated\n\n方案 2: 调整权限策略\n  - 在 policies.json 中添加 elevated 权限\n  - 或使用 sudo 执行特定操作\n\nPAT-078: Subagent agentId 限制\n--------------------------------------\n方案 1: 修改权限策略\n  - 在 policies.json 中允许特定 agentId\n  - 示例: {\"sessions_spawn\": {\"allowed\": [\"novel-reviewer\"]}}\n\n方案 2: 修改小说评审脚本\n  - 使用默认子代理（不指定 agentId）\n  - 在子代理内部再进行专业化分工\n\n方案 3: 创建专门的 Cron 任务\n  - 将小说评审功能拆分为独立任务\n  - 避免在心跳中使用 sessions_spawn\n\n======================================\n自动修复检查\n======================================\n✅ 有写入权限，可以进行配置调整\n\n下一步操作:\n1. 检查上述配置文件\n2. 根据建议调整权限策略\n3. 测试修改后的效果\n4. 如需帮助，请查看相关 Skill:\n   - skills/evolved-cron-health-monitor/SKILL.md\n   - skills/subagent-lifecycle-manager/SKILL.md"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exit