existence.sh` (3.1KB)\n- `evolver/fixes/diagnose-permissions.sh` (3.1KB)\n\n### 预期效果\n- 文件存在性错误: 6 次 → 0 次\n- 权限问题检测时间: 手动 → 自动\n- 系统健康评分: 8.8 → 9.0（修复后）\n\n### 下次进化\n**时间**: 2026-03-08 14:30 (6 小时后)\n**重点**:\n1. 验证权限修复效果\n2. 配置 EvoMap API 认证\n3. 修复 Cron 任务执行模式"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9281473702cf41aca9629cdf","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history && git add -A && git commit -m \"Round 290: 权限问题修复 + 文件存在性检查\n\n- 创建 Skill: evolved-permission-guard\n- 创建脚本: fix-file-existence.sh\n- 创建脚本: diagnose-permissions.sh\n- 诊断 PAT-077~080 权限问题\n- 提供详细修复方案\n- 更新 Pattern Registry\"","workdir":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9d524ab9a32e4848b7685711","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history && git push","workdir":"/root/.openclaw/workspace/evolver_history"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5","usage":{"input":1736,"output":1059,"cacheRead":54784,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57579,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772929906434}}
